            "failure_message": "Acute wrath-crossing only: wrath must cross threshold with arousal clearly elevated, negative valence, and threat not dominating. Smoldering anger is capped so controlled hostility can't masquerade as a surge. Requires restraint collapse (low or sharply dropping inhibitory_control, with low trait self_control making it easier). Still demands a large wrath delta so it reads as a true surge, not drift."
